title: Baked Veggie Stuffed Chicken
ingredients: ['15g butter', '70g finely diced acorn squash', '1 green pepper, diced', '1 small onion, finely diced', '1 stick celery, chopped', 'salt and pepper to taste', '4 skinless, boneless chicken breasts', '60g grated Cheddar cheese', '250g plain flour, for coating']
